reviewText: I bought this movie for my Dad, he says he hasn't seen it in a long time and says it's really funny so I can't wait until he gets home so we can watch it with the Fam. And the package came in perfect condition, Brand New Factory sealed & what I'm most happy about is that it got here 3 days earlier cause it said it was gonna arrive on the 25th. So Thank You to the person that shipped it out to me. :)
